710225.description: Raven hires a new personal assistant, thinking she's found the perfect fit. But fear sets in when personal organization turns to personal obsession.

711054.title: Behind Closed Doors 2: Toxic Workplace
711054.description: After landing her dream job, marketing graduate Joy works hard to succeed in her new role but her boss' intentions are anything but professional.

711273.title: Branded & Brainwashed: Inside NXIVM
711273.description: A self-help group simply looking to improve their lives soon finds themselves subjected to a megalomaniac leader who blackmailed, brainwashed, and branded his female members.

711321.title: TMZ No BS: Hollywood's Biggest Lies
711321.description: TMZ dives into the biggest stories in hollywood. From the rise of Kim Kardashian to the fall of Jussie Smollett. Discover the true stories as the lies are brought to light.

713116.title: A Neighbor's Vendetta
713116.description: After an affair leads to an accidental death, a married couple moves away to start all over only to find trouble next door.

713119.title: Alarmed
713119.description: When a couple plans a getaway, things go terribly wrong when their son is held hostage in their high tech home and the only way to save him is to kill or be killed.

713166.title: Frankie Meets Jack
713166.description: Sparks fly when Frankie meets Jack, the veterinarian who rescues her dog from near death. They seem destined to be together, but there's one problem: Jack is already engaged.

713221.title: Safe Word
713221.description: When a newlywed couple decides to open their relationship to strangers, the wife quickly realizes her husband is a sadistic monster whose fetishes might destroy her.

715028.title: Love You To Death: The Jodi Arias Story
715028.description: LOVE YOU TO DEATH: JODI ARIAS is an examination of the murder of Travis Alexander, and the subsequent trial that turned Jodi Arias into social media's first true femme fatale.

722270.title: Deadly Estate
722270.description: When a hotel manager is wrongly accused of killing the soon-to-be new owner’s son, she must use her hospitality skills to prove her innocence.

722979.title: Best Friend
722979.description: Trisha and Jamie have been best friends since grade school. Jamie tries to keep Trisha’s new love interest apart, even if it costs someone’s life.

723258.title: TMZ No BS: Conor McGregor
723258.description: Brash, fearless & as loud as they come – Conor McGregor’s ascent to superstardom caught everyone by surprise, but the very formula that made him may ultimately lead to his downfall

724359.title: Tainted
724359.description: After surviving an abusive mother, a young woman can’t shake her past demons and continuously runs into problems with men—until she finally snaps.

724369.title: Street Logic
724369.description: This drama follows Key and Dubb, two ex-convicts who decide to try and change their luck. Their new plan? Start robbing from the queenpin, Moon.

725056.title: Loyalty
725056.description: All hell breaks loose when it’s revealed to drug dealer Buttons that his girlfriend was once the longtime side piece of his biggest competitor.

100000301.title: Castaways
100000301.description: In a post apocalyptic world, two women find themselves shipwrecked on a deserted island. As they fight to survive, the experience bonds them in ways they could never have imagined.

100000334.title: Queen of Cocaine
100000334.description: In a crime world built for men, only one woman was daring enough to pave the way for the most infamous Colombian cartels: Griselda Blanco, the Godmother of Cocaine.

100000371.title: The Threat Next Door
100000371.description: When an overworked single mother hires a friendly neighbor to babysit her daughter, she begins to face increasingly strange and threatening situations.

100000585.title: Gone Before Her Time: Brittany Murphy
100000585.description: Scene-stealing starlet Brittany Murphy was destined for Hollywood’s A-list until her untimely and mysterious death turned out the lights on her lifelong dreams.

100000629.title: Butch Cassidy and the Wild Bunch
100000629.description: When the infamous Butch Cassidy and his deadly band of outlaws pull off a high-dollar train robbery, the legendary Pinkertons raise a deadly posse to hunt them down.

100000719.title: Surprise
100000719.description: Convinced his wife is cheating on him with his best friend, a husband goes off the deep end into a conspiracy, only to find himself unprepared for what comes next.

100000747.title: Dead Hot
100000747.description: After a ghost hunt gone wrong, students of witchcraft Vanessa Hudgens and GG Magree travel to Salem, Massachusetts to seek out proper mentorship from experts in witchcraft.

100000963.title: Blood, Sweat and Cheer
100000963.description: A mother seeking to relive her glory days poses as her teen daughter to join a high school dance team.

100000965.title: A Good Man
100000965.description: Struggling in the aftermath of his wife's affair, a man's attempt at a new relationship begins to spiral out of control when he notices familiar signs.

100001048.title: Bury the Bride
100001048.description: Bride to be June’s bachelorette party turns deadly when her blood thirsty fiancé and his friends show up to crash the party.

100001214.title: Murder at the Murder Mystery Party
100001214.description: An aspiring actress thinks a murder mystery party will be the perfect way to break into the LA scene — until she realizes that the murder is real, and she’s being framed for it.

100001219.title: TMZ No BS: Cardi B
100001219.description: Stripper. Reality Star. Rap Legend. Cardi B became an undeniably talented and entertaining celebrity, but with her rise came headlines, cheating scandals, court cases, and beefs.

100001250.title: Marry F*** Kill
100001250.description: After their friend Beth’s suicide, five estranged friends learn Beth bequeathed them her ancestral home - but unbeknownst to them, they’ve inherited something far more sinister.

100001401.title: No Way Out
100001401.description: Forced to take on a double murder case after the suspect threatens his family, attorney Brian Nelson begins to unravel the facts and learns the case isn’t what it seems.

100002070.title: Bad Cat
100002070.description: A profane house cat must deal with the arrival of his illegitimate son, an accidental killing, his owner's eviction and more within the course of a day of debauchery and mayhem.

0300008637.title: Mike Tyson Mysteries
0300008637.description: The adult animation classic series featuring the voice talents of Mike Tyson and Norm MacDonald sees the champion boxer taking on weekly mysteries!

0300010091.title: Kitchen Commando
0300010091.description: Chef Andre Rush brings the might of the military to restaurants across America as he takes up the mission to save the struggling service industry.

0300007638.title: Life
0300007638.description: Created by multi-award-winning writer Mike Bartlett, Life explores the human capacity for connection in an increasingly splintered society. Manchester, England. The residents of a large suburban house go about their very different lives. The walls that divide their flats keep them apart. But life has a way of bringing people together. Like all ordinary lives, theirs are filled with the extraordinary. And as their stories begin to intersect, hidden secrets connect these characters in ways that could never have been anticipated.

0300008956.title: Freddy's Nightmares
0300008956.description: Wes Craven’s brainchild Freddy Krueger leaves Elm Street for spine-tingling trips through the horrors of new worlds and dark nooks of the imagination.

0300007896.title: The Freak Brothers
0300007896.description: After smoking a magical strain of weed and falling into a 50-year slumber, the Freak Brothers and their outspoken cat awaken in the 2020s and attempt to adjust to the bizarre rat race of modern times.

0300009078.title: A Man Called Hawk
0300009078.description: Returning to his hometown, a mysterious man for hire walks a fine line at the edge of the law as he pursues his quest to "do good for good people."

0300007629.title: Meet, Marry, Murder
0300007629.description: Wedded couples vow to stay together, until death do they part. This series looks at what happens when a bride or groom causes their beloved’s demise.

0300005163.title: The Masked Singer
0300005163.description: Celebrity performers, costumed to conceal their identities but dropping hints along the way, compete each week as one is eliminated and unmasked.
